// Comprehensive time series decomposition methods:
// - Classical decomposition (additive/multiplicative)
// - STL (Seasonal and Trend decomposition using Loess)
// - MSTL (Multiple Seasonal-Trend decomposition)
// - X-11/X-13 ARIMA-SEATS style decomposition
